ome.smuggler.core.types

Class ImportBatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.types.ImportBatch

  • public class ImportBatch
extends java.lang.Object
    Groups multiple import runs into a single batch. Currently only used for collapsing email notifications so that users get one outcome notification per batch as opposed to one per import run.
